"&kappname; dođe sa terenom za obuku. <link linkend=\"howto\">Igra na ovom "
"terenu</link> je najlakši način da započnete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the ball into the hole with the least possible hits."
msgstr "Ubaciti lopticu u rupu sa što je manje moguće udaraca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play "
#| "hands-on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the "
#| "basics. This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the "
#| "tutorial, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Tutorial</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"&kolf;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play hands-"
"on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the basics. "
"This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the tutorial, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutorial</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;-ov game-play je jednostavan. Najlakše je naučiti igrati tako što "
"jednostavno igrate, i stoga je uključen teren za tutorijal koji vas provodi "
"kroz osnove. Ovo poglavlje će vas provesti kroz taj tutorijal. Da biste "
"započeli tutorijal, odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoć</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Tutorijal</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hitting the Ball"
msgstr "Udaranje loptice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter "
#| "aims in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the <keycap>Left "
#| "Arrow</keycap> (counterclockwise) or <keycap>Right Arrow</keycap> "
#| "(clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgid ""
"To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter aims "
"in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the &Left; arrow "
"(counterclockwise) or &Right; arrow (clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgstr ""
"Da biste naciljali, možete postaviti miš iza loptice tako da je palica "
"okrenuta u pravcu u kojem želite da loptica ode, ili pritsnuti jednu od "
"tipki <keycap>Lijeva strelica</keycap> (smjer suprotan smjeru kazaljke na "
"satu) ili <keycap>Desna strelica</keycap> (u smjeru kazaljke na satu), da "
"biste rotirali palicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To rotate the putter more quickly with the keyboard, hold down &Shift; while "
"pressing or holding the arrow keys. To rotate more slowly, hold down &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Da biste rotirali palicu brže pomoću tastature, pristisnite &Shift; i jednu "
"od strelica u isto vrijeme. Da biste rotirali palicu sporije, držite &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or <keycap>Down Arrow</"
#| "keycap> key. The longer you hold down the key or button, the more "
#| "strength the putt will have. It will take practice to get a good feel for "
#| "speed."
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or &Down; arrow key. The "
"longer you hold down the key or button, the more strength the putt will "
"have. It will take practice to get a good feel for speed."
msgstr ""
"Da biste udarili lopticu, pritisnite i držite ili &LMB; ili <keycap>Donja "
"strelica</keycap> tipku. Što duže držite tipku ili dugme, palica će imati "
"više snage. Treba dosta vježbe da se stekne osjećaj za brzinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To stop the putt while you are still holding moving the putter back in your "
"stroke, press &Esc;."
msgstr "Da biste zaustavili udarac dok još pomjerata palicu, pritisnite &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hit the ball into the hole to move on to the next."
msgstr "Ubacite lopticu u rupu da biste prešli na sljedeću."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slopes"
msgstr "Padine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in "
#| "an expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, "
#| "so the brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner "
#| "of the hole. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
#| "Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see an arrow that points in the "
#| "direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgid ""
"Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in an "
"expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, so the "
"brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner of the "
"hole. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see an arrow that points in the "
"direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgstr ""
"Padine su zakrivljene površine terena po kojima se loptica kotrlja na "
"očekivani način. Svjetlo terena se nalazi na gornjoj lijevoj strani, tako da "
"će najsvijetlije padine gurati lopticu prema gornjem lijevom uglu rupe. "
"Odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži "
"informacije</guimenuitem></menuchoice> da biste vidjeli strelicu koja "
"pokazuje u pravcu u kojem će se loptica kotrljati niz padinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tutorial hole, hit the ball onto the upward-pointing slope and let "
"it roll into the cup to move onto the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Na tutorijalu o rupama, udarite lopticu u pravcu padine nakošene uzbrdo i "
"pustite da se otkotrlja u rupu da biste prešli na sljedeću."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directions"
msgstr "Smjerovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
#| "elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kappname;. Hit "
#| "the ball into the hole."
msgid ""
"On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
"elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kolf;. Hit the "
"ball into the hole."
msgstr ""
"Na sljedećoj rupi, eksperimentirajte sa drugim tipovima padina. Postoje "
"eliptične, vertikalne, horizontalne i dijagonalne padine u &kappname;-u. "
"Ubacite lopticu u rupu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steepness"
msgstr "Strmost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you "
#| "choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>, the steepness of the slope will appear as a "
#| "number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
#| "into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgid ""
"The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you choose "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, the steepness of the slope will appear "
"as a number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
"into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Naredni tutorijal ima dvije padine različitih strmosti. Ako odaberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži informacije</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, strmost padine će se prikazati u vidu broja od "
"1-8, gdje je 8 najstrmije a 1 najmanje strmo. Ubacite lopticu u rupu i "
"pređite na sljedeću rupu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Walls"
msgstr "Zidovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Balls bounce of walls as one would expect them to, with a little bit of "
"dampening. Deflect the ball off the walls and into the cup to advance to the "
"next hole."
msgstr ""
"Loptice se odbijaju od zidove onako kako očekujete, sa malo prigušenja. "
"Odbijte lopticu od zid i u rupu da biste prešli na sljedeću."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107 index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles and Sand"
msgstr "Bare i Pijesak"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles"
msgstr "Bare"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles are blue. When your ball rolls into a puddle, a penalty stroke is "
"added to your score and you must then choose where you want to take your "
"next shot from: either next to the puddle or from the same place as where "
"you just took the last shot."
msgstr ""
"Bare su plave boje. Kada se vaša loptica otkotrlja u baru, dobijate kaznu u "
"vidu oduzimanju bodova, a onda morate odabrati odakle želite izvesti vaš "
"sljedeći udarac: s mjesta pored bare ili s mjesta odakle ste uputili "
"posljednji udarac prije nego što je loptica upala u baru."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand"
msgstr "Pijesak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand is yellow. Balls roll through sand very slowly."
msgstr "Pijesak je žut. Loptice se kotrljaju kroz pijesak jako sporo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hit the ball around the puddles and through the sand into the hole to "
"continue to the next tutorial hole."
msgstr ""
"Udarajte lopticu tako da upada u bare i pijesak i ubacite je u rupu da biste "
"prešli na sljedeći tutorijal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117 index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windmills"
msgstr "Vjetrenjače"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Windmills are compound objects with brown border walls and a moving arm on "
"one side. Half-walls create the opening to the windmill, which the black arm "
"swings across. It takes practice to be able to time the stroke of the ball "
"to pass through the opening. Hit the ball through the windmill into the hole "
"to continue."
msgstr ""
"Vjetrenjače su objekti sa smeđim zidovima i pokretnim dijelom na jednoj "
"strani. Polu-zidovi stvaraju prolaze kroz vjetrenjaču, preko kojih se okreće "
"crni dio. Potrebna je vježba da biste tempirali udarac tako da loptica prođe "
"kroz otvor. Udarite lopticu tako da prođe kroz otvor i upadne u rupu da "
"biste nastavili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Black Holes"
msgstr "Crne Rupe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit "
#| "and ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to "
#| "the speed your ball was going. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see which "
#| "Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out "
#| "of the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
#| "corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then "
#| "eject the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgid ""
"When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit and "
"ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to the speed "
"your ball was going. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see which "
"Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out of "
"the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
"corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then eject "
"the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Kada vaša loptica upadne u crnu rupu, biva transportovana na izlaz i "
"izbačena pod uglom izlaza brzinom direktno proporcionalnom brzini kojom je "
"išla vaša loptica. Odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži informacije</guimenuitem></menuchoice> da biste "
"vidjeli koja crna rupa vodi na koji izlaz i kojim smjerom će loptica izaći "
"kroz izlaz. Obruči oko crnih rupa su iste boje kao i odgovarajući izlazi. "
"Ubacite lopticu u crnu rupu, koja će onda izbaciti lopticu u rupu da biste "
"prešli na sljedeću."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125 index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Floaters"
msgstr "Plutajuće platforme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands on it. Floaters' "
"speeds vary. This one is a pretty slow floater, but you still must time your "
"shot so you can go over the wall and into the cup."
msgstr ""
"Plutajuće platforme nose loptice koja padnu na njih. Brzine plutajući "
"platformi variraju. Ovo je poprilično spora platforma, ali i dalje morate "
"tempirati udarac da bi loptica prešla preko zida i upala u rupu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bridges"
msgstr "Mostovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges are simple - they just lift the ball above the things below them, "
"like slopes, sand, and puddles. They can have brown walls on their perimeter."
msgstr ""
"Mostovi su jednostavni - oni jednostavno podižu lopticu iznad stvari ispod "
"sebe, kao što su padine, pijesak i bare. Mogu imati smeđe zidove s vanjske "
"strane."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, Strategije i Savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kappname;'s basic features."
msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kolf;'s basic features."
msgstr "Ovdje je detaljan opis osnovnih opcija &kappname;-a."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Započinjanje igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start a game, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This opens a dialog "
#| "where you can configure your new game."
msgid ""
"To start a game, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This opens a dialog "
"where you can configure your new game."
msgstr ""
"Da biste započeli igru, odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ovo otvara dijalog u "
"kojem možete konfigurisati svoju novu igru."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a player to your game, click the <guibutton>New Player</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dodali igrača u svoju igru, kliknite na dugme <guibutton>Novi "
"igrač</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "To change the name of the players, change the text in the text boxes."
msgstr ""
"Da biste promijenili imena igrača, promijenite tekst u tekstualnim okvirima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a player, click the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button next to "
"the player's name."
msgstr ""
"Da biste uklonili igrača, kliknite na dugme <guibutton>Ukloni</guibutton> "
"koje se nalazi odmah pored imena igrača."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Course name:"
msgid "Course Page"
msgstr "Ime terena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list "
#| "box on the left of this page. &kappname; comes with many built-in courses "
#| "that you can play."
msgid ""
"To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list box "
"on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses that you "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"Da biste odabrali teren na kojem želite igrati, kliknite na odgovarajuću "
"stavku u listnom okviru na lijevoj strani ove stranice. &kappname; dolazi "
"opremljen sa mnogo terena na kojima možete igrati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
#| "<guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and "
#| "choose the course file in the file dialog."
msgid ""
"To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and choose "
"the course file in the file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dodali teren koji ste preuzeli ili napravili, kliknite na dugme "
"<guibutton>Dodaj...</guibutton> na dnu ove stranice, i odaberite datoteku "
"terena u dijalogu za odabir datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can choose whether or not this game will be played in "
"<guilabel>Strict mode</guilabel>. In strict mode, there is no undo, moving "
"holes, or editing of the course. This mode is generally for competition. "
"Only in strict mode are high scores kept."
msgstr ""
"Na ovoj stranici možete odlučiti da li želite da se ova igra igra u "
"<guilabel>Strogi režim</guilabel>. U strogom režimu, nema poništavanja "
"poteza, pomjeranja rupa, ili uređivanja terena. Ovaj režim se koristi "
"uglavnom za takmičenje. Najbolji rezultati se čuvaju samo u strogom režimu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saved Games"
msgstr "Spašene igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress "
#| "and save them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved "
#| "games include the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, "
#| "and the scores of the players."
msgid ""
"&kolf; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress and save "
"them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved games include "
"the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, and the scores of "
"the players."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; može čuvati historiju vaših rundi koje su i dalje u progresu i "
"spasiti ih na disk tako da ih možete učitati i igrati kasnije. Spašene igre "
"uključuju trenutnu rupu, imena i boje svih igrača u igri, i rezultate igrača."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Your Game"
msgstr "Spašavanje vaše igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To save your game while still playing, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. If you have "
#| "not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
