msgid ""
"To save your game while still playing, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. If you "
"have not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
"to save to."
msgstr ""
"Da biste spasili vašu igru dok još uvijek igrate, odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spasi igru</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Ako još uvijek niste spasili nijednu igru, bit ćete pitani u "
"koju datoteku je želite spasiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Your Game"
msgstr "Učitavanje vaše igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To load the game that you saved, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Load...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can then "
#| "choose the saved game to open."
msgid ""
"To load the game that you saved, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You can "
"then choose the saved game to open."
msgstr ""
"Da biste učitali igru koju ste sačuvali, odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Učitaj...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Onda možete odabrati koju spašenu igru želite da otvorite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practicing"
msgstr "Vježvanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a few features that make practicing your golf easier. These "
"features are not enabled during strict mode."
msgstr ""
"Postoji nekoliko opcija koje olakšavaju vježbanje. Ove opcije nije moguće "
"korisiti prilikom igranja u strogom režimu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "Poništi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To undo a bad shot, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
