#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu contains many menu items for switching to "
"different holes that are quite self explanatory. See the <link linkend=\"go-"
"menu\"><guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu reference</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Idi</guimenu> meni sadrži mnoge stavke za prebacivanje na druge "
"rupe čija su imena dobri opisi njihovih funkcija. Pogledajte <link linkend="
"\"idi-meni\"><guimenu>Idi</guimenu>reference menija</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Putting Options"
msgstr "Opcija ubacivanja loptice u rupu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link "
#| "linkend=\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgid ""
"&kolf; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link linkend="
"\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; ima nekoliko načina za ubacivanje loptice u rupu. Osnovni način "
"je <link linkend=\"hitting\">opisan ispod</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse is enabled by default. This means that whenever the mouse is "
"moved, the putter aligns to the line between the mouse and ball."
msgstr ""
"Miš je uključen od instalacije programa. Ovo znači da kad god se miš "
"pomjeri, palica se poravna sa linijom između miša i loptice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable "
#| "mouse putting by unchecking <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable mouse "
"putting by unchecking the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Ako preferirate korištenje korištenje tastature i strelica, možete "
"isključiti miš tako što otkačite opciju <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Omogući pomjeranje palice mišem</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Putting"
msgstr "Napredno ubacivanje loptice u rupu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Advanced putting can be enabled by checking "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
#| "Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This putting mode is slightly more "
#| "challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
#| "either the mouse or keyboard."
msgid ""
"Advanced putting can be enabled by checking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
"Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This putting mode is slightly "
"more challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
"either the mouse or keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Napredno ubacivanje loptice u rupu može biti uključeno tako što zakačite "
"opciju <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uključi napredno "
"ubacivanje loptice u rupu</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ovaj metod je malo "
"teži od uobičajenog klikni-i-drži načina, i može biti korišten sa mišem ili "
"tastaturom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "To putt in this mode:"
msgstr "Da biste ubacili lopticu u rupu u ovom modu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key once to begin the "
#| "swing. The putting indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will "
#| "start filling up with a color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key once to begin the swing. The putting "
"indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will start filling up with a "
"color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i pritisnete tipku <keycap>Strelica Dolje</keycap> jednom da biste "
"zamahnuli. Pojavit će se indikator udarca, mjerilo snage će se početi "
"popunjavati nekom bojom, koja se mijena tokom punjenja mjerila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key when the strength "
#| "gauge has filled up the amount that you want. The farther around the "
#| "circle the strength gauge has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. "
#| "It takes practice to be able to get the correct strength on putts."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key when the strength gauge has filled up "
"the amount that you want. The farther around the circle the strength gauge "
"has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. It takes practice to be able "
"to get the correct strength on putts."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ili pritisnute tipku <keycap>Strelica Dolje</keycap> kada se "
"mjerilo snage napunilo do količine koju želite. Što se krug oko mjerila "
"snage više napuni, to će udarac biti snažniji. Potrebna je vježba da bi se "
"postigla odgovarajuća snaga prilikom udaraca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this, the color in the putting indicator will start to wind down back "
"to where it started."
msgstr ""
"Nakon ovoga, boja u indikatoru udarca će se početi vraćati nazad odakle je "
"krenula."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key again when the "
#| "strength-indicator is as close as possible to the center line of the "
#| "putting indicator."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key again when the strength-indicator is as "
"close as possible to the center line of the putting indicator."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ili pritisnite tipku <keycap>Strelica Dolje</keycap> ponovo kada se "
"indikator snage bude nalazio što je bliže moguće centralnoj liniji "
"indikatora udarca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer the final click (or key press) is, the more true the putt is to "
"the original line."
msgstr ""
"Što je finalni klik(ili pritisak tipke) bliži, to će udarac biti više "
"poravnat sa originalnom linijom."

