msgstr ""
"Prebacite se u mod za uređivanje korištenjem <menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> da dodate novu rupu na kraj terena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can restore a hole to a blank state, similar to when it was first "
#| "created, by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"You can restore a hole to a blank state, similar to when it was first "
"created, by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Možete vratiti stanje rupe nazad na početno, kao kada je prvi put kreirane, "
"odabirom <menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Očisti</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two items will appear on new holes: a cup, and a white ball. The white ball "
"marks where players' balls start the hole."
msgstr ""
"Na novim rupama se pojave dva predmeta: rupa, i bijela loptica. Bijela "
"loptica označava mjesto početka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Basics"
msgstr "Osnove uređivanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:622
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The basic building block of &kappname; courses is the <quote>object</"
#| "quote>. Holes are made up of a bunch of objects. Objects can be moved to "
#| "any location, and the different kinds of objects each have different "
#| "properties you can set."
msgid ""
"The basic building block of &kolf; courses is the <quote>object</quote>. "
"Holes are made up of a bunch of objects. Objects can be moved to any "
"location, and the different kinds of objects each have different properties "
"you can set."
msgstr ""
"Osnovni gradivni blok &kappname;-ovih terena je <quote>predmet</quote>. Rupe "
"se sastoje od mnogih predmeta. Predmeti se mogu pomjerati na bilo koju "
"lokaciju. Sve vrste predmeta imaju različite osobine koje možete postavljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start editing a hole, toggle the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or press "
#| "the pencil icon on the toolbar. To leave editing mode, uncheck this menu "
#| "item (or the toolbar icon)."
msgid ""
"To start editing a hole, toggle the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or press the pencil "
"icon on the toolbar. To leave editing mode, uncheck this menu item (or the "
"toolbar icon)."
msgstr ""
"Da biste počeli sa uređivanjem rupe, mijenjajte status stavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rupa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, ili prisnite ikonu olovke na alatnoj traci. Da biste napustili "
"mod uređivanja, isključite ovu stavku(ili ikonu na alatnoj traci)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Objects"
msgstr "Dodavanje Predmeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new object to the course, choose its name in the list box labeled "
"<guilabel>Add object:</guilabel>. The object will appear in the center of "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dodali novi predmet na teren, odaberite njegovo ime iz liste "
"označene sa <guilabel>Dodaj predmet:</guilabel>. Predmet će se pojaviti u "
"centralnom dijelu terena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges and signs will cover up new objects if they were already in the "
"center of the hole."
msgstr ""
"Mostovi i znakovi će prekriti nove predmete ako su ti objekti već bili u "
"centru rupe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving and Resizing Objects"
msgstr "Pomjeranje i promjena dimenzija predmeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move your mouse cursor over the object that you want to move, and the mouse "
"cursor will change to a hand cursor. Then click and drag the object to where "
"you want it."
msgstr ""
"Pomjerite kursor miša na objekat koji želite pomjeriti. Sada će se kursor "
"promijeniti u oblik ruke. Kliknite i povucite predmet na mjesto gdje ga "
"želite postaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles, sand, floaters, bridges, and signs can be resized by dragging the "
"small circle at their lower-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Bare, pijesak, plutajuće platforme, mostovi i znakovi mogu promijeniti svoje "
"dimenzije povlačenjem malog kruga u donjem desnom uglu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Walls can be moved by clicking and dragging their endpoints, or you can move "
"the whole wall by clicking and dragging on the middle part of the wall as "
"normal."
msgstr ""
"Zidovi se mogu pomjerati klikanjem i povlačenjem njihovih krajnjih tačaka, "
"ili možete pomjeriti cijeli zid tako što kliknete na središnji dio i "
"povučete ga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objects' Settings"
msgstr "Postavke predmeta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Objects' properties can be changed in the area at the lower-right corner "
#| "of the &kappname; window. To edit an object, move your mouse cursor over "
#| "it until the cursor changes to the hand cursor. Then click. Various "
#| "controls for that object will appear in the lower-right corner of the "
#| "&kappname; window."
msgid ""
"Objects' properties can be changed in the area at the lower-right corner of "
"the &kolf; window. To edit an object, move your mouse cursor over it until "
"the cursor changes to the hand cursor. Then click. Various controls for that "
"object will appear in the lower-right corner of the &kolf; window."
msgstr ""
"Osobine predmeta mogu biti promijenjene u donjem desnom uglu &kappname;-ovog "
"prozora. Da biste uredili neki predmet, pomjerajte kursor miša dok ne "
"promijeni oblik u oblik ruke. Onda kliknite. Pojavit će se razne kontrole za "
"taj predmet u donjem desnom uglu &kappname;-ovog prozora."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Hole Settings"
msgstr "Opšte postavke rupe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit general hole settings, click an area of the hole that is not covered "
"by an object. When this is possible, the cursor will be the normal pointer "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"Da biste uredili opšte postavke rupe, kliknite na površinu rupe koja nije "
"prekrivena nekim predmetom. Kada je to moguće, kursor će se vratiti u "
"normalni oblik."

#. Tag: guilabel
